@startuml
actor Admin as Actor
participant ClassManager
participant AdminAPI
participant Database

Admin as Actor -> ClassManager : View classes
ClassManager -> AdminAPI : getClasses(semesterId)
AdminAPI -> Database : Query classes for semester
Database --> AdminAPI : Return class list
AdminAPI --> ClassManager : Class data
ClassManager --> Actor : Display classes

Admin as Actor -> ClassManager : Increase class limit
ClassManager -> AdminAPI : increaseClassLimit(classId, increment)
AdminAPI -> Database : Update class limit
Database --> AdminAPI : Confirmation
AdminAPI --> ClassManager : Success response
ClassManager --> Admin as Actor : Display updated limit
@enduml
